Confirm user has read the rules, enter their ID into database
with elo and reputation fields, elo starts at 1000, rep starts at 0

let users enter a queue for matchmaking using their ID

if queue is more than 1 index, pop queue at 0 twice 

send users with popped ID match confirmations

if both confirm
    start game
else
    randomize queue positions of both



Game start

both players pick character

coin flip for who bans first

winner bans 1

loser bans 2

winner picks last 2


both players click button to signify game over
both sides report who won

if conflict, try again
if conflict for 3 in a row, end game

else winner bans 2 and loser selects next stage

play next game

once bo3 won, adjust elo and exit